<%# Mark Dead confirmation modal — replaces the native confirm() dialog
    that used to gate the markDead action. Permadeath in a Nuzlocke is
    irreversible: the modal shows the group nickname + warning copy +
    two clearly-distinct buttons. CONFIRM DEATH is the destructive path
    (gb-btn-danger); CANCEL is the safe out (default styling).

    Wired by `dashboard` Stimulus controller:
    - `openMarkDeadModal(event)` populates + shows
    - `confirmMarkDead()` fires the PATCH
    - `closeMarkDeadModal()` hides without firing
    - The MARK DEAD button on the pokemon modal calls
      `dashboard#openMarkDeadModal` instead of the old `dashboard#markDead`. %>
<div data-dashboard-target="markDeadModal"
     class="hidden"
     style="position: fixed; inset: 0; z-index: 60;">
  <div data-action="click->dashboard#closeMarkDeadModal"
       style="position: absolute; inset: 0; background: rgba(15, 56, 15, 0.85);"></div>

  <div style="position: relative; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; min-height: 100vh; padding: 16px;">
    <div class="gb-modal" style="max-width: 440px;"
         role="dialog"
         aria-modal="true"
         aria-labelledby="mark-dead-modal-title"
         data-controller="modal-a11y">
      <div class="gb-modal-title">
        <span id="mark-dead-modal-title">MARK AS DEAD</span>
        <button data-action="click->dashboard#closeMarkDeadModal"
                class="gb-modal-close"
                aria-label="Close modal">&times;</button>
      </div>

      <div style="padding: 12px 4px 4px;">
        <div style="font-size: 14px; margin-bottom: 10px;">
          <span data-dashboard-target="markDeadNickname" style="color: #e8a0a0;"></span>
        </div>

        <div style="font-size: 11px; color: var(--d2); line-height: 1.6; margin-bottom: 16px;">
          This permanently marks every linked pokemon in this group as dead and removes the group from all teams. <strong style="color: var(--d1);">Nuzlocke runs are irreversible.</strong>
        </div>

        <div style="display: flex; gap: 8px; justify-content: flex-end;">
          <button type="button"
                  data-action="click->dashboard#closeMarkDeadModal"
                  class="gb-btn gb-btn-sm">
            CANCEL
          </button>
          <button type="button"
                  data-action="click->dashboard#confirmMarkDead"
                  class="gb-btn-danger gb-btn-sm">
            CONFIRM DEATH
          </button>
        </div>
      </div>

      <input type="hidden" data-dashboard-target="markDeadGroupId">
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
